(12, 'Technical support', '   1.Good communication\r\n2.Strong analytical skills\r\n3.Fundamentals of software security\r\n4.Detail oriented\r\n5.Ability to adhere to processes and procedures.\r\n6.Ability to work independently with little management\r\n7.Have a strong passion for emergin', '1', '<p>Should have good command over any programming language (C, C++ etc..) and good knowledge of HTML, JAVA Script will be an add on benefit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Must be comfortable working with Night Shifts</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Data validation, cleaning, re-coding, formatting, merging and restructuring, integrating Open ended coding&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keeps the project manager updated with the progress on the team tasks&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>- Make / Receive calls from customers relating to tecjnical support / application support queries<br />\r\n- Maintain Client SLAs<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>&lt;p&gt; Fresher to 6 months of experience&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Any Technical Graduate. B.Tech / B.E. / MCA&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; 2017 or 2018&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;</p>\r\n', '2018-07-28', 2, 'opened', '2018-07-25 11:20:20'),
